#EmoryHealthCares #HealingInvisibleWounds #emoryveterans

#ad Veterans and Service members sacrifice so much for our country, and often deal with invisible wounds that can be hard to address. That’s why the Emory Healthcare Veterans Program is such an amazing resource. This two-week intensive program provides evidence-based treatment customized to each individual’s unique needs and goals. Participants receive as much therapy in two weeks as they would typically get in a year and learn about yoga, medications, sleep, wellness, healthy coping skills, and communication techniques. Best of all, it’s offered at no cost to the warrior or their family. If you’re a post-9/11 veteran or service member, and you need help, please consider signing up today. #veteransupport #invisiblewounds EmoryHealthCares #HealingInvisibleWounds #emoryveterans
